                    "body": "The following patch implements an option that be be used to skip closing of the session. The default is to close it. The patch has been made against revision 14153 of http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/svn\/framework\/standard\/trunk\/library\/Zend\/Controller\/Action\/Helper\/Redirector.php.",
